{
  "stem": "1354.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They changed to I don't remember what, because when I was a couple of years ago in Poland, I went there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And one was on [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And right away, she started to-- she was trying to get a place to live in her own-- you know, it was hers, the parents.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Her father passed away before the war and her mother during the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Anyhow, so we went to one of the homes now on [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the-- the janitor knew her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she let us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we slept in her kitchen, the three of us, on the floor, for quite some times, until she got into her other building.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She got a permission to get-- we got at that time, like, like [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was a-- a kitchen, and a bedroom, and a-- a bathroom, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Inside, it was a mother and a thing, so we slept on the floor until she-- we got into the-- to that place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And my brother, whoever he-- whoever he met, if he didn't have where to-- to-- to live, he was bringing him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They were sleeping on the floor in our place, people, after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that's how I met my husband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because I had a cousin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He's not alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He passed away-- he was 46 years old-- of cancer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he was like a brother with him in Mauthausen, because my husband was in Mauthausen, Gusen I, Gusen II.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And he-- they both saved each other's life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And after the war, my cousin, of course, was my brother's cousin, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We-- we met him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And my brother says to my cousin, you come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "There was not too many relatives left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "If you found a cousin, you were happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "You come and live with me in my place.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
